<p>Monet and Gardner became engaged in December 2017 and welcomed little Gio into the world on Sept. 29, 2019. </p>

<p>While Daniella and Andrew talk all things parenthood on their Adulting like a Mother Father podcast, Andrew is gearing up to relaunch the clothing brand Gafton, a passion project he created with his childhood best friend and professional football player, Kenny Wiggins.</p>

